        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued August 7 at 8:15PM EDT by NWS Gaylord MI</headline>
        <description>At 815 PM EDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm over
Alpena, moving east at 15 mph.

HAZARD...Nickel size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor hail damage to vegetation is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Alpena and Devils Lake.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
